  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: ef4120e8d7cc4784ba80e7aeb2d6d58d, type: 3}
  m_Name: Bragi_AboutSigyn
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  Repeatable: 0
  Lines:
  - Text: I remember a second voice, the one who told me to kill the ravens and free
      my father. Was that my mother?
    Speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 4f97ef8596ffbe84c8329bcee3fa66b3, type: 2}
  - Text: Hm, a difficult question. She calls Loki, her husband, your father. That
      feels like claiming motherhood for you, but just as much she may not.
    Speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 221624e13721edf47a3982f9e2ec5bd5, type: 2}
  - Text: Can you tell me who she is?
    Speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 4f97ef8596ffbe84c8329bcee3fa66b3, type: 2}
  - Text: Ah, the beautiful and nurturing Sigyn, brave healer and protector of all.
      She took care of Loki after one of his pranks and fell in love with him.
    Speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 221624e13721edf47a3982f9e2ec5bd5, type: 2}
  - Text: Since his capture following the death of Baldur, she has been his watchful
      guardian.
    Speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 221624e13721edf47a3982f9e2ec5bd5, type: 2}
  - Text: She sounds incredible.
    Speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 4f97ef8596ffbe84c8329bcee3fa66b3, type: 2}
  - Text: That she is, little Lie. Among the best of us, I dare say.
    Speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 221624e13721edf47a3982f9e2ec5bd5, type: 2}
  OnFinished:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
